    >[ ] ship the dependency frontier as a built-in named query $ dependency-clean open actions, every predecessor closed — the GTD next-action computed instead of curated. the daily agenda already embeds this condition; extract it as its own invocable view so it composes $ +library #019f26c1-734e-71aa-b8f0-b0c06a7f0f8d
